<font face="华文中宋" size="40" color="#000000">将重要的梦想放进箱子</font>

207
00:13:08,260 --> 00:13:13,980
<font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#000000">{\an8}箱に乗せ 大切な夢</font>

